data.description: Welcome home! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of this inviting city home. The main level boasts a seamless flow, from the living room to the kitchen, making it perfect for both everyday living and entertainment. You’ll love the hardwood floors throughout! The full bathrooms on each floor provide convenience and privacy, while the large primary bathroom is a luxurious retreat. Step outside to your fully fenced backyard, where you can enjoy outdoor dining, gardening, or simply relax. With a full basement and attic, you'll have plenty of room to store your belongings, ensuring a clutter-free living space. The updated electrical system ensures safety, giving you peace of mind for years to come. You'll be close to all the amenities, including shops, restaurants, and public transportation. This home is the perfect blend of urban convenience and modern comfort. Don't miss your chance to make this charming city home your own. Schedule a viewing and make this gem your new address.
